sources.title: Detective Kitty O'Day
sources.description: A high-energy, screwball whodunit with feisty Jean Parker in the title role. On board for the whacky ride are Peter Cookson, Veda Ann Borg and Tim Ryan who along with Victor Hammond co-wrote the screenplay. Directed by William Beaudine. Released in 1944. Complete print

metadata.Plot: When a girl and her boyfriend are suspected of murdering her employer, they have to clear their names and find the real killer.
metadata.Actors: Jean Parker, Peter Cookson, Tim Ryan
